						               													<description>Everternal is a world of fantasy, adventures and dangers.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the year 1420 C.E. (post Calamity) the legendary mage Pharanor, wielding the mighty Soul Stone, decides to face a recent mysterious threat that has been taking over and corrupting the creatures and lands of Everternal: the Darkness.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As the last member of the arcane protectors, the Magi Council, whom swear to protect the world after the end of the Calamity, Pharanor gather 3 mighty heroes from all around the world with the hope they could aid him on his journey.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The old mage summons the heroes to his tower, in the Bright Citadel of Kalahad, so together they can follow and seek the path of ruin which Darkness leaves behind to discover the source of the evil that threatens the Everternal.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;desConfronto is a 1 - 5 players &amp;quot;LCG&amp;quot; Cardgame where you take on the role of 1 of the 4 most iconic D&amp;amp;D classes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each class has an asymmetric deck of action cards (attack, defense, draw, extra action, and &amp;ldquo;signature&amp;rdquo; moves), which the player will play with to perform powerful attacks and combos by rolling dices in order to purify de corrupted creatures and animals corrupted by the mysterious Darkness that plagues the world of Everternal.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In a thrilling campaign where players advance from level to level, defeating creatures and collecting the shards of corrupted Soulstones in order to use it to buy new skills, potions and traps, our heroes reach the source of corruption to face the great evil that is threatening the world.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
